    note for TapeDecoder "Progressive: fetch 512 KB prefix (doubling) into PSRAM, scan, withhold last entry of a partial window until confirmed; DMP/HTAP/TAP-v2 converted to TAP v1 on the fly; engine freed after each window"
    note for tapclean_engine "Loader-ID fast path identifies the loader from the CBM boot block so identified tapes scan pause+CBM+that loader only; unidentified tapes run all scanners with an early exit at 97 pct coverage"
